note right of strategy_documents
One workspace can hold multiple structured strategy documents,
including IDEATION and VALUE_PROPOSITION.
Each document keeps its own chat thread and section set.
end note

note right of workspaces
Idea Foundry is now available as a dedicated UI surface.
Its pipeline board now renders explicit empty states unless persisted
source artefacts exist. Prospecting persists normalized source records,
Proto-Idea Extraction persists claimed source-processing rows plus
downstream proto-ideas, and later stages can now build on real
traceable pipeline storage instead of placeholders.
end note

