note right of prospecting_configurations
Stores the persisted Prospecting Configuration UI state,
the latest prospecting-agent review payload, and the
normalized result-record set supplied to the next
review run and populated by Prospecting Execution.
latest_review_json stores the Prospecting Agent's latest strategy assessment.
last_result_records stores the latest normalized execution results and feeds
the next Prospecting Agent review so strategy quality can evolve over time.
Prospecting reviews now depend on shared registry visibility
for agent_definitions and prompt_configs, while the FastAPI
gateway keeps its own runtime persistence schema for sessions,
runs, checkpoints, and audit history.
end note

note right of knowledge_bases
Knowledge bases partition retrieval scope for admins and agents.
Files are registered before processing, embeddings stay traceable
to the parent file, and background jobs drive asynchronous ingestion.
end note

