note bottom of agent_test_runs
Stores evaluation-specific transcript execution, scorecards,
and review artifacts, while canonical product conversation
execution remains in agent_runs. The admin run-detail API
returns related transcript, score, annotation, and snapshot
records directly for reviewer inspection.
end note

